Adopt a robust, highly available Microsoft Azure cloud infrastruture that's entirely secure.  Simplified security management is provided with role-based capabilties, that are baked right into the product.  Mobile devices are effortlessly managed with the same security settings and group policies as laptop and desktop devices.

Microsoft maintain platform integrity with a strictly controlled and tested approach to Microsoft's Azure cloud server patching and maintenance.  You don't have to worry about platform robustness, the status of servers or the resources to maintain them, servers are managed for you.

¬Microsoft Azure, Office 365 and Dynamics CRM are ISO, government and specialist industry compliant.  Products conform to the strictest standards and adhere to regulatory requirements.  Detailed information is available from Microsoft's Trust Centres, designed to provide market defining transparency as well as data protection, security and independent verification official accreditation facts, that are easily accessible.

¬Manage mobile devices and desktop devices with the Microsoft suite of management tools.  Microsoft Intune enables management of mobile devices, mobile applications and PC's from the cloud and Microsoft System Center supports management of desktop real-estate.  Provide employees with access to corporate applications and resources from virtually anywhere on almost any device, while helping to keep corporate information secure.

¬Microsoft platforms incorporate an advanced security model for controlling access to data.  'Role based' privileges ensure users can only perform actions relevant to them.  With access so easily controlled, it's easy to segment responsibilities for analysing and extracting insights from data, across many different industry scenarios and partner organisations also.
